{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d7b0fff05","title":"毛泽东关于中南军区应增加打虎预算给谭政等的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ede0c16861","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":18,"articleId":"8d7b0fff05"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e53eee5aea","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于中南军区应增加打虎预算给谭政等的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05"},{"id":"0613ee37d2","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05"},{"id":"f4f9d16766","type":"appellation","text":"谭政同志并告剑英：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05"},{"id":"e4d78cfb3d","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日电收到。你们军区打虎预算据中南局最近电告增至打大虎八百，这比你们过去的数字是增大了，但和华东军区的一千六百相比，仅及其一半。实际上华东军区大虎将来可能打至二千五百至三千。你们基本上应与他们看齐，但可稍迟一会再增加，并须启发下面同志自动增加，始不觉得太勉强。特别是华南军区系统可能打大虎一千以上，中小虎万数，而他们定得很低，勇气不旺。最近看了四十八军打虎渐多，应即以之教育全军。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05"},{"id":"64fd346565","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东二月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05"}],"page":{"id":"9739ed3f38","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8d7b0fff05","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}